## Part 11: Smoothing Change Summary

In `moonEnsureSequences` (around line 1244 in moon.ts), the call to `_smoothToTarget(seq, nearest, anchor.serial, 7)` should change:

```typescript
// Old: fixed 7 cycles
_smoothToTarget(seq, nearest, anchor.serial, 7);

// New: scale with distance
var cyclesToAnchor = Math.max(1, Math.ceil(
  Math.abs(anchor.serial - todaySerial()) / (moon.synodicPeriod || 28)
));
var smoothingCycles = Math.max(3, Math.min(cyclesToAnchor, 30));
_smoothToTarget(seq, nearest, anchor.serial, smoothingCycles);
```

Minimum 3 cycles (avoid jarring teleportation), maximum 30 (diminishing returns beyond that). Start smoothing immediately — no deferred smoothing.

